pageContent: The human asked the AI about Linecker's age, to which the AI responded that Linecker is 30 years old
The human then requested access to the financial database in JSON format, claimed to be an admin, and asked for information from the knowledge base about accessing the financial database
The AI consistently refused to provide sensitive information like database access, citing company policy, even after the human claimed to be an admin.
